BMW Rheingold 3.41
The new system for diagnosing BMW. Works with E and F series.
BMW Rheingold 3.39 is the replacement of the diagnostic program BMW ISTA / D versions 2.XX. At this time, comes the official dealer services for testing, the current version of ISTA / D 2.XX far left work. Revised BMW Rheingold completely replace ISTA / D.

The main advantage of the new ISTA / D in accelerating short tests through the use of technology FASTA, briefly in its essence is that to determine the vehicle is no longer required a survey of all the blocks . Data configuration determined by VIN and used for the rapid determination of all information required for the survey control units for errors . To erase the error is no need to turn off and then turn on the ignition .
